the Node resource. You can see it by using the kubectl describe command as in the
following listing.
$ kubectl describe nodes
Name:       minikube
...
Capacity:                       
  cpu:           2               
  memory:        2048484Ki       
  pods:          110             
Allocatable:                       
  cpu:           2                  
  memory:        1946084Ki          
  pods:          110                
